16 agency of another state or of the federal government, or a report
17 prepared by an independent accounting firm, which on being accepted
18 is considered for all purposes as an official report of the
19 Commissioner; and
20 4. Summon and examine under oath a key individual or employee
21 of a licensee or authorized delegate and require the person to
22 produce records regarding any matter related to the condition and
23 business of the licensee or authorized delegate.
24
ENGR. S. A. TO ENGR. H. B. NO. 3521 Page 27

