2 Commissioner shall have full and complete access to, all records the
3 Commissioner may reasonably require to conduct a complete
4 examination. The records shall be provided at the location and in
5 the format specified by the Commissioner, provided, the Commissioner
6 may utilize multistate record production standards and examination
7 procedures when such standards reasonably achieve the requirements
8 of this section.
9 C. Unless otherwise directed by the Commissioner, a licensee
