15 B. In order to fulfill the purposes of this act, the
16 Commissioner shall be authorized and encouraged to establish
17 relationships or contracts with NMLS or other entities designated by
18 NMLS to enable the Commissioner to:
19 1. Collect and maintain records;
20 2. Coordinate multistate licensing processes and supervision
21 processes;
22 3. Process fees; and
23 4. Facilitate communication between states and licensees or
24 other persons subject to this act.
ENGR. S. A. TO ENGR. H. B. NO. 3521 Page 31

1 C. The Commissioner shall be authorized and encouraged to
2 utilize NMLS for all aspects of licensing in accordance with this
3 act, including, but not limited to, license applications,
