21 SECTION 14. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
22 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1564 of Title 6, unless there is
23 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
24
ENGR. S. A. TO ENGR. H. B. NO. 3521 Page 32

1 A. Applicants for a license shall apply in a form and in a
