21 SECTION 24. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
22 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1574 of Title 6, unless there is
23 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
24
ENGR. S. A. TO ENGR. H. B. NO. 3521 Page 55

1 A. A licensee shall file a report with the Commissioner within
2 one (1) business day of the licensee becoming aware of the
