4 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1579 of Title 6, unless there is
5 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
6 A. Every licensee shall forward all money received for
7 transmission in accordance with the terms of the agreement between
8 the licensee and the sender unless the licensee has a reasonable
